14132.「あー！ あいつですー！\n あいつが 手強い旅芸人ですよー！:
Ahh! <if_woman>Her<else>Him<endif> again!
It's that strong-looking minstrel!

14133.「フォッフォッフォ 感じます……。\n 私の弟弟子ポルファンと 同じオーラを。:
Oh ho ho... You have the same kind of
litheness as my disciple, Polfan...
Yes... I can feel it...

14134.「あなたは ポルファンの弟子ですね。\n 役立たずのゲイザーより お強いようで。:
You are his student, yes? You're much stronger
than that worthless Gazer. That pleases me...
I much prefer those who are strong.

14135.「でもね 残念です。私 嫌いなんですよ。\n くだらん芸をする 旅芸人っていうの:
But what a pity. I loathe them...those
minstrels who use such trivial tricks. How do
I put this...I simply cannot stand them.

14136.「もうね 好き嫌いの問題ではないです……。\n 生理的にダメ。つまらん芸とか ナ:
It's no longer a matter of preference...they physically sicken me. It's pointless and nonsensical! How could anyone find them
entertaining...?

14137.「もうね ホント世の中どうかしてますよ。\n どいつもこいつも つまらん芸で笑っ:
The world is truly mad. It's madness that
everyone laughs at such trite tricks, yet my
sense of humor goes unappreciated?

14138.「で 結論。なにが言いたいのかというとですね。\n 旅芸人は この世から消えてく:
So this is my solution. All minstrels are to
disappear from this world. If they don't...
then I'll just kill them all.

14139.「キャッ キャッ♪\n ボクたちも 殺したいですー♪: Kee, hee! We want to kill you, too! ♪

14140.「ボクたち ルルルリーチ様の特訓で\n ちょー 強くなったぜー♪:
Thanks to Master Relulu's training, we've
gotten a looooot stronger! ♪

14142.「私 好きなんですよ。命をかけた戦いが。\n 芸も 似たようなものですよね？\n:
Battles where your life is on the line...I
very much enjoy them. Aren't tricks the same?
Oh ho ho... Come. Let's have some fun!

14143.「あなた また来たんですか？\n あれだけ 痛めつけてさしあげたのに\n まだ:
So you've come again? Still you desire
even more of my lashings of love?

14144.「フォッフォッフォ うれしいです。\n 私 好きなんですよ。弱い者をいたぶるのが:
Oh ho ho...how wonderful. I quite enjoy
pummeling on the weak. How thoughtful
of you to entertain this hobby of mine.

14145.「フォッフォッフォ。さあ 楽しませてください。\n 私は まだまだ 満足していま:
Come...let us continue having fun.
I'm still not satisfied!

14146.「……フォッフォッフォ。お強いですね。\n しかし 悲しいことですが 才能ある者:
Oh ho ho...you are indeed strong.
Sadly...those with talent are often faced
with discrimination.

14147.「私は ポルファンより 才能がありましたが\n 魔物の芸など ウケるわけなく ど:
I was more talented than Polfan... But no matter where I went, my performances proved unpopular... Not a single soul would
appreciate them.

14148.「しかし 自分より才能のない多くの旅芸人が\n 成功している……。私は絶望しまし:
But so many other untalented minstrels saw
success...it broke me. Before long, I began
to resent them...

14149.「フォッフォッフォ。才能が あったところで\n 世の中は それを正しくは評価しま:
Oh ho ho... Just because you have talent does
not mean it will be properly appreciated...

14150.「あなたは 自分の才能が認められなくても\n くさらずに 笑いの道を極められます:
Even if your talents are never recognized...
could you still walk the path of laughter?<yesno><close>

14151.「フォッフォッフォ。そうでしょうね……。\n そのように 強い心を持った旅芸人な:
Oh, ho, ho... It's just as I thought.
It's impossible for such a strong-hearted
minstrel to exist in this world...

14152.「フォッフォッフォ。ムリですよ……。\n そのように 強い心を持った旅芸人など\:
Oh, ho, ho... It's impossible.
There's not a minstrel in the world who
possesses such a strong heart...
